image_analysis.description: A photograph of an industrial or mechanical utility room. The image shows a complex network of pipes, including copper lines and white insulated pipes. A large white rectangular control box or equipment unit is mounted on metal struts. A vertical white insulated pipe in the foreground has a yellow label. The floor is concrete, and there is a floor drain visible. In the background, electrical panels and conduit are visible.
